    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer754821221" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12437623835468424237">This was probably the first piece of Chinese literature I&apos;d read which struck something deep within me, despite its utterly alien cultural feel. The translation can, at times, be a little bit stilted (although this seems to be endemic to most translated Chinese literature; Chinese and English are <b>very</b> different languages and do not translate well to each other). It is pretty much this drama which led me to start exploring loads of other Chinese literature ranging from the ancient to the new. </span>
  <span id="freeText12437623835468424237" style="display:none">This was probably the first piece of Chinese literature I'd read which struck something deep within me, despite its utterly alien cultural feel. The translation can, at times, be a little bit stilted (although this seems to be endemic to most translated Chinese literature; Chinese and English are <b>very</b> different languages and do not translate well to each other). It is pretty much this drama which led me to start exploring loads of other Chinese literature ranging from the ancient to the new. </span>
  <a data-text-id="12437623835468424237" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


