    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1299404473" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4449201979798133227">The concepts of this culture&apos;s view of the afterlife was entirely new to me, as was the extent of a girl&apos;s isolation and subservience. While I was not taken by the performance piece which underlies the whole book, it does make a framework in which the main character&apos;s story can unfold. Recommend.</span>
